---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me" description="About Dom Kirby — cybersecurity professional, content creator, and technology enthusiast.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">

    <!-- Header: headshot + name -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start gap-8 mb-10">
      <img
        src="/headshot.png"
        alt="Dom Kirby"
        class="w-36 h-36 rounded-full object-cover ring-4 ring-green/40 flex-shrink-0"
      />
      <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Dom Kirby</h1>
        <p class="text-green font-medium">Cybersecurity, Cloud & AI for SMBs | CISSP, SSCP | People-First Leader</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none
      prose-headings:text-white
      prose-a:text-green
      prose-strong:text-white
    ">
      <p>I work at the intersection of technology, business, and people. At Pax8, I lead a team of engineers, strategists, and operations professionals who deliver technical outcomes for thousands of managed service providers. My focus is on cloud, cybersecurity, and how AI can transform the way services are delivered at scale.</p>
      <p>
        I spend a lot of time helping others cut through complexity—whether that’s driving results for partners, shaping how vendors think about security and AI, or sharing insights on stage at conferences. Just as important, I’m always learning. Every conversation, project, and challenge is an opportunity to pick up something new and carry it forward.
      </p>
      <p>
        At the core, I’m passionate about connecting innovation to real-world outcomes. That means building strategies that don’t just look good on paper, but work in practice.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work, I keep things grounded with family, community, and a steady curiosity for what’s next.
      </p>
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Feel free to reach out via the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>, or connect with me
        on social media.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
